<Group labelreference="L1" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">restart; with(plots):</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L3" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">twopi := evalf(2*Pi);</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">mod1 := x -&gt; x - floor(x+.5);</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L59" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal"></Text-field>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal">* Define the standard map...</Text-field>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal"></Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L5" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">f := (x,y) -&gt; x + g(x,y);</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">g := (x, y) -&gt; y + K/twopi * sin(twopi*x);</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L105" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">f_i := (x, y) -&gt; x - y;</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">g_i := (x, y) -&gt; y - K/twopi * sin (twopi * f_i(x, y));</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L114" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal"></Text-field>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal">* Check if this is the correct reverse</Text-field>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal"></Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L108" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">xx[0] := .4; yy[0] := .4;</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L107" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">N := 10; K:=2;</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">for n from 0 to N-1 do</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" linebreak="space" spaceabove="0" rightmargin="0" bullet="none" firstindent="0" linespacing="0.0" pagebreak-before="false" leftmargin="0" alignment="left" initial="0" spacebelow="0">  xx[n+1] := mod1(f(xx[n], yy[n]));</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" linebreak="space" spaceabove="0" rightmargin="0" bullet="none" firstindent="0" linespacing="0.0" pagebreak-before="false" leftmargin="0" alignment="left" initial="0" spacebelow="0">  yy[n+1] := mod1(g(xx[n], yy[n]));</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">end do:</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">for n from 0 to N-1 do</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" linebreak="space" spaceabove="0" rightmargin="0" bullet="none" firstindent="0" linespacing="0.0" pagebreak-before="false" leftmargin="0" alignment="left" initial="0" spacebelow="0">  xx[N + n+1] := mod1(f_i(xx[N+n], yy[N+n]));</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" linebreak="space" spaceabove="0" rightmargin="0" bullet="none" firstindent="0" linespacing="0.0" pagebreak-before="false" leftmargin="0" alignment="left" initial="0" spacebelow="0">  yy[N + n+1] := mod1(g_i(xx[N+n], yy[N+n]));</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">end do:</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L106" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">xx[2*N]; yy[2*N];</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L109" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal"></Text-field>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal">These values are the same as the initial conditions - the inverse is correct.</Text-field>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal"></Text-field>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal">We will calculate the evolution of a dense cloud of initial conditions around (0,0). First create the cloud...</Text-field>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal"></Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L70" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">Nx := 75; Ny := 75; Nt := 10; Lx := 0.01; Ly := 0.01;</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L98" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">K := 2;</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L71" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">xs := Array(1..Nx*Ny, -Nt..Nt): ys := Array(1..Nx*Ny, -Nt..Nt):</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L72" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">k := 1;</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">for i from 1 to Nx do</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" linebreak="space" spaceabove="0" rightmargin="0" bullet="none" firstindent="0" linespacing="0.0" pagebreak-before="false" leftmargin="0" alignment="left" initial="0" spacebelow="0">  for j from 1 to Ny do</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" linebreak="space" spaceabove="0" rightmargin="0" bullet="none" firstindent="0" linespacing="0.0" pagebreak-before="false" leftmargin="0" alignment="left" initial="0" spacebelow="0">    xs[k, 0] := mod1(-Lx/2 + Ly * (i-1)/(Nx-1));</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" linebreak="space" spaceabove="0" rightmargin="0" bullet="none" firstindent="0" linespacing="0.0" pagebreak-before="false" leftmargin="0" alignment="left" initial="0" spacebelow="0">    ys[k, 0] := mod1(-Ly/2 + Ly * (j-1)/(Ny-1));</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" linebreak="space" spaceabove="0" rightmargin="0" bullet="none" firstindent="0" linespacing="0.0" pagebreak-before="false" leftmargin="0" alignment="left" initial="0" spacebelow="0">    k := k + 1;</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" linebreak="space" spaceabove="0" rightmargin="0" bullet="none" firstindent="0" linespacing="0.0" pagebreak-before="false" leftmargin="0" alignment="left" initial="0" spacebelow="0">  end do;</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" linebreak="space" spaceabove="0" rightmargin="0" bullet="none" firstindent="0" linespacing="0.0" pagebreak-before="false" leftmargin="0" alignment="left" initial="0" spacebelow="0">end do;</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L111" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal"></Text-field>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal">The cloud of initial conditions has been initialized. Integrate this cloud forward and backward in time.</Text-field>
<Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal"></Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L83" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">n := 0;</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">pp := seq([xs[i, n], ys[i, n]], i=1..Nx*Ny):</Text-field>
</Input>
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">p[0] := plot([pp], style=point, color=black, symbol=point):</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L25" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">for n from 0 to Nt-1 do</Text-field>
